Media Explorer Web Remote
------------------------

Prototype of a webremote for media explorer.

Features:

 * Allows you to search your local media and play it.
 * Navigate media explorer
 * Control the media player

Usage:
  mex-webremote [OPTION...] - Media explorer web remote

Help Options:
  -h, --help       Show help options

Application Options:
  -b, --bind       Bind to a particular ip address
  -p, --port       Port to listen to http requests on
  -d, --debug      Dispay debugging info
  -a, --auth       username:password


Open your browser to http://<hostname or ip address>:port/

All api is subject to change.
